Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.60,0:00:11.94,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,猛烈的雨令心頭震動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.58,0:00:16.41,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,像那日一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.41,0:00:22.91,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,直至昨日我一直追逐着的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.49,0:00:27.45,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在仍然相信它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.56,0:00:34.33,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,沒終結的防衛也不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.97,0:00:41.80,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你繼續凝望着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.54,0:00:44.80,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,STAND UP TO THE VICTORY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.38,0:00:50.81,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,迎接過不知多少個早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.42,0:00:53.51,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,將來一定會抓緊給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.85,0:00:56.05,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,STAND UP TO THE VICTORY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.49,0:00:57.95,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,因為在那對面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.39,0:01:05.82,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,即使甚麽也沒有都不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.26,0:01:13.97,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,只要懷着沒人能代替你的笑臉

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.52,0:01:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，艾寶目擊到在敵人中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.15,0:01:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稱為加里，丹的大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.02,0:01:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他害怕稱為戰場的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.06,0:01:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個令人瘋狂的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.03,0:01:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只那樣，他也懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.93,0:01:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是否人的記仇心制造出戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.43,0:01:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，胡索他…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.00,0:01:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰士的光輝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.47,0:01:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.71,0:01:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，因為害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.15,0:01:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而要我默默等死，我更加害怕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.05,0:01:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.92,0:02:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和為支援戰鬥機就太小型了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.52,0:02:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要逃的還可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.72,0:02:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機師是個小孩，他在怕呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.19,0:02:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.46,0:02:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何沙伯特和加里會被打敗呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.33,0:02:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因為太疏忽大意吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.41,0:02:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是甚麽陣形？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.41,0:02:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我教曉你戰士是甚麽來吧！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.45,0:02:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三對一，沒有勝望了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.12,0:02:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四面的彈射台被破壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.95,0:02:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在能發射的上身部份只得這部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下身部份呢？還有兩三部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！總得設法掩護胡索！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.26,0:02:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！不要被打中呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.74,0:02:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面還有人生存嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.85,0:03:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？ 是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.32,0:03:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要愛惜生命呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.76,0:03:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，為何你一定要戰斗呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.43,0:03:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…不想卡迪珍娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.77,0:03:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪貝德小姐和大家死！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.97,0:03:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子有點誤會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.84,0:03:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡迪珍娜小姐，你聼到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣很快會無子彈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.58,0:03:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.25,0:03:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把吊臂移向左邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.82,0:03:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要突然提出呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.39,0:03:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說多少時的方向吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.99,0:03:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十時的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.79,0:03:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.03,0:03:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想被你殺死啊，胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.03,0:03:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打不中敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次這裡被瞄準的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.37,0:04:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人一飛過來就攻擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.94,0:04:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色傢伙的結合部件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算搬去哪裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.08,0:04:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有幫手的地方嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.52,0:04:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把卡美昂運輸車駛去前面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.62,0:04:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有方法帶走所有部件嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.06,0:04:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果再沒有轟炸就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.20,0:04:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞中溫達利，傑拉戰斗小隊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰斗方法，我很有興趣看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.74,0:04:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是上身部份，要快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.54,0:04:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.98,0:04:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結合後它的武裝會被強化了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.69,0:04:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟着下身部份就發射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.93,0:04:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.06,0:05:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下身部份發射了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.90,0:05:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又有一架嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那種地方，你竟敢…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.48,0:05:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.06,0:05:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能回來呢，胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.71,0:05:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索被戰爭拉去了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.21,0:05:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭…把胡索帶走了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.59,0:06:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅，把下身部份裝上卡美昂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.26,0:06:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.39,0:06:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！聼到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.93,0:06:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會再射出一身部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐多一陣，聼到嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.73,0:06:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.85,0:06:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.12,0:06:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有敵人入侵呀！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.13,0:06:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史特萊加！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會再讓你結合的了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.83,0:06:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然無錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.77,0:06:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伏低！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.24,0:06:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.62,0:07:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，不能出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.05,0:07:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別動！動的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.16,0:07:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兩人就會成為槍下亡魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.06,0:07:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別迫我那樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.29,0:07:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是甚麽人！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.96,0:07:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧爾，寧古伯爵，和我一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.27,0:07:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是卑斯柏的黃色夾克部隊！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.23,0:07:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會跟你去的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.77,0:07:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是黃色夾克部隊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂得駕駛小型車吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.48,0:07:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行！開槍射這男人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.65,0:07:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,槍已跌在地上，要試試嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.53,0:07:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恕我無禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要多想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.80,0:07:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照我說話去做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.01,0:08:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中尉！請掩護我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.98,0:08:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支持下去呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.25,0:08:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.70,0:08:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百古！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被打中了！不能再飛呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.50,0:08:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請想辦法幫我呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百古！放棄機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用逃生囊吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.05,0:08:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停手呀！百古！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.58,0:08:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.19,0:08:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰士不可以怕死的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.56,0:08:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小隊長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.03,0:08:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送你一程吧！百古！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.48,0:09:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑斯大柏…連自己人也殺嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.53,0:09:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！放下它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！胡索！你聼到嗎！不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪貝德小姐！你聼到嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射出下身部份後，拜託你掩護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.27,0:09:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔！發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.80,0:09:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.44,0:09:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要成功結合呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.95,0:09:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下半身又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用V模式結合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.77,0:10:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結合完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是白色機動戰士！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.51,0:10:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高達是反抗的象徵這個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.62,0:10:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就由我溫達利，傑拉來鞏衡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.96,0:10:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在反抗聯邦軍體制的是我們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.03,0:10:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真正的高達的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.47,0:10:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它應該和我們聯手的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.71,0:10:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好機會！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.93,0:11:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也應該能瞄準的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.90,0:11:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.31,0:11:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杜拉布！回轉翼的馬力下降了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.21,0:11:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麽事呀！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.35,0:11:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是白色傢伙做的好事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.02,0:11:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！我們太不熟悉它的武器轉變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.59,0:11:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杜拉布！跟我來！知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.93,0:11:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃去其他地方吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你，這樣我就不痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.04,0:11:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中尉，我講過多少次我是無用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那由我來決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.99,0:12:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去看看嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.52,0:12:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人，追那機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.59,0:12:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫卡迪珍娜，路施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.97,0:12:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在才知道你的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說了就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.14,0:12:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帶了水來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.81,0:12:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飲吧，水呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，對不起，多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.25,0:12:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.05,0:12:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來喇，胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.72,0:12:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，辛苦你了  多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.39,0:12:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎蒂，沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.47,0:12:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽事呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.80,0:12:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是寧古伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵他戰死了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.27,0:12:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，但也關差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.78,0:13:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被卑斯柏的間諜帶回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.41,0:13:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被帶走了！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.15,0:13:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你傾慕的卡迪珍娜小姐也被帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.62,0:13:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡迪珍娜小姐也…是甚麽回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.82,0:13:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.42,0:13:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何會變成那樣的！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.76,0:13:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們太大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.69,0:13:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會那樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的機動戰士部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.31,0:13:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是聲東擊西的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.94,0:13:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了拐走伯爵嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.68,0:13:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麽！我中計了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.78,0:13:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既是說，不是你贏了呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.52,0:13:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是甚麽意思！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.75,0:13:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我講得無錯吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.29,0:13:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麽，為何你不幫手呀！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.06,0:13:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家也很努力的了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.86,0:13:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麽，為何會那樣呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.03,0:13:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你請就容易囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有戰斗的意義啊！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有戰斗的不只是你呀！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.23,0:13:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使你們吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.60,0:14:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也無補於事的吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們選錯戰斗的對手了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的不是胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.08,0:14:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.26,0:14:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡的話，大家也會變得古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.29,0:14:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回去卡沙呢里亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.49,0:14:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人已從基地裡逃了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.30,0:15:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為有必要派遣格達路隊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐低！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.01,0:15:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的戰斗方式是尊重騎士道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,溫達利，傑拉上尉的戰斗方式啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.22,0:15:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.16,0:15:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還自以為了不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.99,0:15:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰斗後我們也要鬆弛一下的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.90,0:15:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做甚麽呀！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.06,0:15:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說話了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.97,0:15:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了自己享樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.90,0:15:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就俘虜女人回來啊，中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.84,0:15:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自持是女皇陛下的弟弟就亂來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.88,0:15:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.75,0:15:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那和我沒關係！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.55,0:15:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是你那樣想啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.62,0:16:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也在拼命的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.36,0:16:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我那樣做完全不過份！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是打算玩那女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.10,0:16:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才帶她回來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.80,0:16:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位先生不是那種人來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已馴服了地球的女人嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.44,0:16:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則，為何不在叛軍的基地裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.58,0:16:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺死這女人呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.52,0:16:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你原諒我部下的無禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.66,0:16:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.29,0:16:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你向在格拉斯基利的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.49,0:16:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達斯羅，華歌上校報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.73,0:16:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,溫達利，傑拉戰斗小隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.66,0:16:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會拼死戰至最後一部機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.07,0:16:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.63,0:16:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的騎士道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.94,0:16:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎會呢！我還有很多計劃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.58,0:16:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騎士道始終只是理想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.69,0:17:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小型車向日落的方向去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.22,0:17:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要找到就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.76,0:17:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要避免在黑夜搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.23,0:17:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.60,0:17:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在湖那邊會合！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.93,0:17:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎！胡索！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.87,0:17:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道，羅美洛叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.07,0:17:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會沒事的，羅美洛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.44,0:17:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子一定會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.51,0:17:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則他今日就不會那樣戰斗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.71,0:17:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，伯爵也承認那孩子的天份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.88,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是剛才的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.60,0:18:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃走之後的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.98,0:18:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.92,0:18:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從哪裡來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.33,0:18:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我親手把戰士的尊嚴和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.48,0:19:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的部下也抛棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.08,0:19:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高達！！被嘴咒的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你下地獄吧！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.99,0:19:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.19,0:19:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是個不應該
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.56,0:19:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們面前出現的名字！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.13,0:19:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是甚麽人！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下地獄吧！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.98,0:19:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右手的雷射盾受損了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.98,0:19:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會被打敗！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.69,0:19:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃不掉的！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.00,0:20:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴魯勤炮…來福鎗…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷射劍也沒有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.44,0:20:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你完了！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.48,0:20:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.75,0:20:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會讓你走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.63,0:20:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是白色機動戰士的機師！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.93,0:20:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.53,0:20:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你設置陷阱，所以我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.84,0:20:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要面對這樣的現實嗎…！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.08,0:20:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還想時常玩耍的小孩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.92,0:21:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在這種地方…做這種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.89,0:21:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.76,0:21:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩…不應該打仗的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.90,0:21:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣做的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.00,0:21:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家也會變得很可笑的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.87,0:21:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.51,0:21:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你離開機動戰士會比較好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是想做才去做的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.41,0:21:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現實…竟然是這樣殘酷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.45,0:21:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走開！快遠離我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.49,0:21:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走呀！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.79,0:21:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.82,0:22:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽…

